{"tid":692253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(申請Nowtv前請三思)Nowtv電腦隨身睇苦主區(70004)","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T10:30:54.000Z","uid":4609,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"8f26e838ec5c7469115631afdda21262a284cd3d","tid":692253,"uid":4609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"有用電腦睇開Nowtv的人, 都知道Nowtv係一個叫 Microsoft Silverlight呢個垃圾到無倫的player/software去播放所有頻道, 包括免費台同收費台。<br />\n<br />\n首先Microsoft Silverlight呢個垃圾軟件, 絕大部分的瀏覽器都係支援唔到!<br />\n當中包括絕大部分人所用緊的Firefox, Google Chrome, Microsoft edge都係支援唔到。換句話講, 支援到的只有Microsoft Internet Explorer!!<br />\n<br />\n係兩個月前的某一日, 我如常想開IE去睇英超, 但Login完之後, 突然彈出以下Error:-<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/205633_be5c831e7f8489b9b309bf22013dd3aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F205633_be5c831e7f8489b9b309bf22013dd3aa.png&h=f294971c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係電腦完全無更新的情況下, 突然睇唔到波!! 我試過不斷又不斷重新開機, 不斷又不斷搵Window更新, 不斷重新卸載同下載Microsoft Silverlight呢個垃圾軟件, 試左幾廿萬次, 都係唔得。<br />\n我之後上網搜尋, 發覺勁多人有同樣問題!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=now+70004&amp;rlz=1C1GIWA_enHK611HK611&amp;oq=now+70004&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57j0l3.3943j1j7&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dnow%2B70004%26rlz%3D1C1GIWA_enHK611HK611%26oq%3Dnow%2B70004%26aqs%3Dchrome..69i57j0l3.3943j1j7%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8&d=3BdenyTzpX0%2BqmX7tfYxqiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1605ebfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=now+70004&amp;rlz=1C1GIWA_enHK611HK611&amp;oq=now+70004&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57j0l3.3943j1j7&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8</a><br />\n絕大部分人根本解決唔到最後不了了知。但重點係, 可以用電腦睇nowtv, 係我地昂貴月費的其中一個服務黎!!<br />\n<br />\n於是我打1000同客服嘈, 佢俾左兩個link我叫我跟住做。第一條link唔得, 第二link叫我下載勁多軟件去掃瞄/第三方軟件下載Microsoft Silverlight。最後當然都係, 唔得!!<br />\n<br />\n我再打俾1000嘈, 我好簡單咁要求佢可唔可以安排一位技術員去解決我呢個技術上的問題, 最後的答案我超級驚訝: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無!!!</span></span><br />\n佢話公司無軟件技術員!! 我再問佢點解決, 佢不斷主張係我電腦有問題, 話我電腦壞!! 如是者爭論左成個月, 只係話會幫我反映問題, 但都係解決唔到!! 成兩個月睇唔到英超呀屌Nowtv老母, 白俾月費!!<br />\n<br />\n我知一定有人會問, 點解唔用電視去睇? 我兩部電視一部俾我老婆霸住, 一部俾我個仔霸住, 你估我想用電腦睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1000條友叫我用電話隨身睇去睇, 我再屌佢老母, 俾$2xx月費叫我用4吋mon去睇波??<br />\n<br />\n真心呼籲想申請Nowtv的人要三思!! 宜家順利用到電腦睇Nowtv亦都注意小心有一日會出現同樣的問題!!"},{"pid":"d3714bdcc9d1552eb503090924747a28740b4ee6","tid":692253,"uid":23560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n次次都要拎部iPad睇<br />\n電腦無一次係用到嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n咁我交月費嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3302e3943c7536703e4f523ea8e971455e988ccb","tid":692253,"uid":1089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"2018仲用silverlight真係好撚ON9, load到都幾分鐘同你起一次格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ccb9c56bc8066de32a7dd757316830b6f863ad","tid":692253,"uid":31151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"寫信去消委會啦 唔洗同呢間仆街野客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c13b7fdcb85308681922cb7692afe72fd7153e","tid":692253,"uid":57951,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d3714bdcc9d1552eb503090924747a28740b4ee6","tid":692253,"uid":23560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n次次都要拎部iPad睇<br />\n電腦無一次係用到嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n咁我交月費嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"我又幾鍾意用ipad睇<br />\n不過最仆街係之前睇英超只可以限死一個裝置<br />\n一個月先准你轉一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7eed4181bb7391cf3ef8ebbe559b33bb3a275b","tid":692253,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"